{"tid":1736343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"阿里巴巴預計下周二（26日）上市","createTime":"2019-11-18T17:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T17:54:15.000Z","uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1a6b304f10f4035e0288966674b0c8e5a58a5c11","tid":1736343,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:32:42.000Z","msg":"外電報道，阿里巴巴（新上市編號：09988，美：BABA）香港上市國際配售反應不俗，將提早半日截飛，亦即19日（周二）凌晨就會截止認購。早前有消息指，阿里巴巴在國際配售首日已錄足額認購。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指，阿里今日決定提早結束國際配售認購，但依然會在星期三（20日）晚上定價，阿里美股周二收市價將成為其國際配售最終定價。<br />\n<br />\n公開發售方面，阿里將於周三中午截止認購，每股招股價不超過188元。阿里最新孖展認購88億元，超購近3倍。<br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴預計下周二（26日）上市。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2500556/%e3%80%90%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e5%b7%b4%e5%b7%b4%e4%b8%8a%e5%b8%82%e3%80%91%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e5%b7%b4%e5%b7%b4%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b%e9%85%8d%e5%94%ae%e8%b6%b3%e9%a1%8d%20%e6%8f%90%e6%97%a9%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%88%aa%e9%a3%9b?mtc=20023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2500556%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2598%25bf%25e9%2587%258c%25e5%25b7%25b4%25e5%25b7%25b4%25e4%25b8%258a%25e5%25b8%2582%25e3%2580%2591%25e9%2598%25bf%25e9%2587%258c%25e5%25b7%25b4%25e5%25b7%25b4%25e5%259c%258b%25e9%259a%259b%25e9%2585%258d%25e5%2594%25ae%25e8%25b6%25b3%25e9%25a1%258d%2520%25e6%258f%2590%25e6%2597%25a9%25e5%258d%258a%25e6%2597%25a5%25e6%2588%25aa%25e9%25a3%259b%3Fmtc%3D20023&d=iNjGaRjC%2BmHxaGo4xJJZV%2FsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=d053fe65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2500556/%e3%80%90%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e5%b7%b4%e5%b7%b4%e4%b8%8a%e5%b8%82%e3%80%91%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e5%b7%b4%e5%b7%b4%e5%9c%8b%e9%9a%9b%e9%85%8d%e5%94%ae%e8%b6%b3%e9%a1%8d%20%e6%8f%90%e6%97%a9%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%88%aa%e9%a3%9b?mtc=20023</a>"},{"pid":"d6565fc13ce19d893649ab9c61705bdb9065d239","tid":1736343,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T17:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=